  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat",
    "add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes",
    "add the minced garlic and sliced ginger and cook for 1 minute",
    "add the toasted fennel seeds, ground cumin, ground coriander, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper, and cook for 1 minute",
    "add the chopped preserved lemons and cook for 1 minute",
    "add the lamb shoulder and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes",
    "add 2 cups of water to the pot and bring to a boil",
    "reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 2 hours, or until the lamb is tender",
    "shred the lamb with two forks and serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley"
